1
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:11,840
Captain Sun,

2
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:14,280
between 12:00 and 2:00 when the case was reported,

3
00:01:14,280 --> 00:01:15,880
17 large vehicles passed by this road.

4
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:17,640
Only one vehicle didn't get on the highway.

5
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,640
The license plate number is

6
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:19,960
Jiang E94845.

7
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:21,000
According to the surveillance camera,

8
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,200
this vehicle finally disappeared in this logistics park.

9
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,800
It never came out since then.

10
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:31,640
Search separately.

11
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:32,039
Okay.

12
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,020
Northwest corner.

13
00:02:27,200 --> 00:02:28,079
Red truck.

14
00:02:28,480 --> 00:02:29,079
Copy that.

15
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,400
Not unloaded yet.

16
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,140
The truck was just washed.

17
00:02:41,160 --> 00:02:42,820
They shouldn't have gone far.

18
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,640
Excuse me, sir.

19
00:03:10,200 --> 00:03:11,720
I'd like to ask if this truck can...

20
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:13,040
Who are you?

21
00:03:16,440 --> 00:03:16,920
I'm...

22
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,860
Excuse me, sir.

23
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:18,800
Um,

24
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,200
how much to Dagang?

25
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:20,920
I...

26
00:03:20,920 --> 00:03:21,720
I don't smoke.

27
00:03:22,440 --> 00:03:23,840
Well, these days,

28
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,920
my car is getting maintenance.

29
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:26,040
I'm not taking passengers.

30
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:27,160
Find someone else.

31
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:28,079
Come on, sir.

32
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:29,320
Do us a favor.

33
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:30,770
We'll pay you extra.

34
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:31,720
Oh, right.

35
00:03:31,800 --> 00:03:33,280
My client needs it urgently.

36
00:03:33,280 --> 00:03:34,240
Around here,

37
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:36,680
yours is the only car available, right?

38
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,680
You'd better find someone else.

39
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,040
Hey, hey.

40
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:42,160
Sir, don't go.

41
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:42,480
Sir.

42
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:44,210
The people there said Lu Wei...

43
00:03:50,200 --> 00:03:51,200
Forensic.

44
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,200
Take him over first.

45
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:15,720
Okay.

46
00:04:16,640 --> 00:04:17,170
Let's go.

47
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:21,760
Are we interrogating him directly?

48
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:23,530
Let him stew for a while.

49
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:26,280
It's been less than half a day since the incident.

50
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:27,440
His memory is still fresh.

51
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:28,640
Let him think it over.

52
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,810
When the time comes,

53
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,210
he'll crack naturally.

54
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:32,080
Just a little push,

55
00:04:32,080 --> 00:04:33,140
and he'll confess.

56
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,250
Understood.

57
00:04:46,280 --> 00:04:47,159
Still the same.

58
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:48,760
Nothing has changed.

59
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:57,360
Let's go,

60
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:58,080
Lao Yan.

61
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:02,400
If you don't come back soon,

62
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:05,400
I really won't be able to keep that prime spot of yours.

63
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:08,970
You have no idea.

64
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:11,040
Every day, people fight over your desk

65
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,760
like cats and dogs.

66
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:15,140
I fought tooth and nail to save it for you.

67
00:05:16,080 --> 00:05:16,880
I wipe it every day,

68
00:05:16,880 --> 00:05:19,010
even more often than I wash my own face.

69
00:05:20,280 --> 00:05:21,140
Comrade Yan Mi.

70
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:25,890
Rejoin the team.

71
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,250
Don't get stuck in the past.

72
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,090
Get a change of scenery for now.

73
00:05:37,480 --> 00:05:38,740
Are you kicking me out?

74
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:44,170
We will always be partners.

75
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,600
I'll wait for you to come back.

76
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,600
We'll continue fighting together.

77
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,720
It was you.

78
00:06:53,159 --> 00:06:54,920
You killed my parents.

79
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:57,440
Why wasn't it you who died?

80
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,560
Give me the photo.

81
00:07:12,320 --> 00:07:12,880
Yan.

82
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:15,000
It's in the past.

83
00:07:15,280 --> 00:07:16,760
Master's case is closed.

84
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:18,080
The facts are clear,

85
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,040
and the evidence is sufficient.

86
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:20,560
It was Ma Guangfu's deliberate revenge.

87
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,920
No one was behind him.

88
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:23,610
But what about the bomb?

89
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:26,620
He never confessed where the bomb came from.

90
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:29,480
He must be covering for the real culprit behind him.

91
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,010
Only by finding this person

92
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,560
can we find the truth

93
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:34,090
about our master's murder.

94
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,810
The best way to honor our master now

95
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:46,330
is for both of us to do our jobs well.

96
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:50,080
The living expenses you send to Guannan every month,

97
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:51,200
every time he receives them,

98
00:07:51,200 --> 00:07:52,360
he returns them unopened

99
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,400
to the mailroom.

100
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:54,880
Five years,

101
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,530
a full sixty envelopes.

102
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:59,040
Lao Yan.

103
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:02,370
I believe Guannan doesn't truly hate you.

104
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:04,680
He just needs a little more time.

105
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:07,400
Time always moves forward.

106
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:10,520
We can't be trapped in the past forever.

107
00:08:10,680 --> 00:08:12,010
We have to look forward.

108
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:14,440
But for some,

109
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,290
time hasn't moved forward.

110
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:22,800
Master.

111
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,360
Master.

112
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:27,000
The forensics team is checking Lu Wei's truck.

113
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,920
They called and said

114
00:08:27,920 --> 00:08:31,580
human tissue and bloodstains were found on the tires and chassis.

115
00:08:31,760 --> 00:08:32,600
The time is ripe.

116
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,360
Let's go get him.

117
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,360
Take them off him.

118
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:36,840
Yan.

119
00:08:37,039 --> 00:08:37,600
Hurry up.

120
00:08:45,560 --> 00:08:47,490
You thought you ran over a wild dog.

121
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:49,040
Lv Wei.

122
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:51,400
Ask yourself if that's believable.

123
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:53,280
If you ran over a wild dog,

124
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:55,120
why did you run when you saw the police?

125
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:55,640
Lv Wei.

126
00:08:55,760 --> 00:08:57,820
Not taking the chance I give you, huh?

127
00:08:57,840 --> 00:08:58,280
Fine.

128
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:00,440
Hey.

129
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,320
I didn't mean to run.

130
00:09:03,200 --> 00:09:04,440
At first,

131
00:09:04,440 --> 00:09:06,520
I really thought I ran over a wild dog.

132
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:08,380
When I got out to check,

133
00:09:10,920 --> 00:09:12,580
that thing wasn't a dog at all.

134
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:13,970
How fast were you going?

135
00:09:14,160 --> 00:09:15,160
I forgot.

136
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,640
Maybe 70 or 80.

137
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:23,340
Did you stop after hitting it?

138
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,160
Wait a minute.

139
00:09:26,560 --> 00:09:28,280
Did you run over it or hit it?

140
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,720
I ran over it.

141
00:09:30,040 --> 00:09:31,520
I didn't hit it.

142
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,080
When it crashes,

143
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:34,300
there's a bang.

144
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,560
There was no bang.

145
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,320
The car just jolted a bit.

146
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,480
It ran over something.

147
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:40,040
When you got out of the car,

148
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,610
what did the body look like?

149
00:09:41,760 --> 00:09:42,720
Did it have a head?

150
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:43,480
How would I dare

151
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,520
to look closely?

152
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:45,480
It's so scary.

153
00:09:46,640 --> 00:09:47,720
It's so scary.

154
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,680
The killer was brutal

155
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:56,860
and professional.

156
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:57,720
And

157
00:09:57,760 --> 00:09:58,560
they also left

158
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:00,320
a lot of false traces on the body

159
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,520
to confuse us.

160
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:02,640
It shows

161
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:04,800
the killer planned this carefully.

162
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,120
Yes.

163
00:10:06,560 --> 00:10:08,520
The state of the body is shocking.

164
00:10:09,360 --> 00:10:10,890
We have fully confirmed it.

165
00:10:11,240 --> 00:10:11,720
The highway

166
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,080
is not the primary crime scene.

167
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:13,920
However,

168
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,560
the killer transported the body parts

169
00:10:15,560 --> 00:10:16,560
very cautiously,

170
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:17,400
so

171
00:10:17,400 --> 00:10:18,520
the specific details of the crime

172
00:10:18,520 --> 00:10:20,320
are still being reconstructed.

173
00:10:21,560 --> 00:10:22,800
To move the victim,

174
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:25,200
the killer must have used a vehicle.

175
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:26,560
I suggest

176
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,200
we return to the scene

177
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,400
to find a breakthrough.

178
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:30,680
If we find the car used to dump the body,

179
00:10:30,680 --> 00:10:32,480
we can find the person who dumped it.

180
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:33,480
It is now certain

181
00:10:33,760 --> 00:10:36,600
that this is a gruesome murder and dismemberment case.

182
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,200
I announce

183
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:39,120
the immediate establishment of the 5.17 task force.

184
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,440
I will take charge personally.

185
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,720
The specific investigation work

186
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,360
will be handled by the criminal investigation team.

187
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,920
All departments across the bureau

188
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,040
will provide full cooperation.

189
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:47,240
Without further ado,

190
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:49,360
everyone must stay alert

191
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:52,980
and bring the killer to justice as soon as possible.

192
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,000
Help!

193
00:11:02,520 --> 00:11:03,440
Help!

194
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:06,440
Help!

195
00:11:12,120 --> 00:11:12,800
Stay away!

196
00:11:13,680 --> 00:11:14,680
Don't come any closer!
